Package: roadrunner
Title: Fast, Low-Dependency Machine Learning Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9036
Authors@R:
    person(c("Jack", "T."), "Rametta", , "jtrametta@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9841-146X"))
Description: A collection of fast, low-dependency implementations of
    classical machine learning algorithms. Includes 'ares()', a
    Multivariate Adaptive Regression Splines (MARS) fitter using
    Friedman's (1991) fast least-squares forward selection and a
    parallelized knot search built on 'Rcpp' and 'RcppParallel'; and
    'krls()', a Kernel Regularized Least Squares fitter
    (Hainmueller and Hazlett 2014) with a parallelized Gaussian-kernel
    construction and marginal-effect computation.
